   NO.                      Control Enhancement Name
                                                                         LOW         MOD         HIGH

 AU-8       Time Stamps                                                 Select     Select      Select

OT Discussion: Example compensating controls include using a separate system designated as an
authoritative time source. See related control SC-45.
