AU-10 NON-REPUDIATION

                                                                           CONTROL BASELINES
  CNTL                         CONTROL NAME
   NO.                      Control Enhancement Name
                                                                         LOW         MOD         HIGH

 AU-10      Non-Repudiation                                                                    Select

OT Discussion: OT devices may not enforce non-repudiation of audit records and may require
compensating controls. Example compensating controls include physical security systems,
cameras to monitor user access, or a separate device for log collection.
